com.hcl.domino.admin.replication

Enum ReplicationFlags

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ReplicationFlags>
      • com.hcl.domino.admin.replication.ReplicationFlags
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INumberEnum<Short>, Serializable, Comparable<ReplicationFlags>

    public enum ReplicationFlags
extends Enum<ReplicationFlags>
implements INumberEnum<Short>
    Replication flags

    NOTE: Please note the distinction between DISABLE and NEVER_REPLICATE. The former is used to temporarily disable replication. The latter is used to indicate that this database should NEVER be replicated. The former may be set and cleared by the Notes user interface. The latter is intended to be set programmatically and SHOULD NEVER be able to be cleared by the user interface.
